title: chore(android): setup build flavors (#546)
message:
chore(android): setup build flavors (#546)

Added 2 build flavors, dev and prod. Now you've to run the following to build the app,

`react-native run-android --variant=prodRelease` - release version of production
`react-native run-android --variant=prodDebug` - debug version of production
`react-native run-android --variant=devRelease` - release version of dev flavor
`react-native run-android --variant=devDebug` - debug version of dev flavor

You still need to change the host and protocol first in the `client.json` file. It'll be very difficult to automate this, so I chose not to do it.
